Troubleshooting Tips
Issue: Out of Memory Errors

Reduce dataset size in generate_data.py
Increase driver memory: .config("spark.driver.memory", "4g")
Issue: Slow Performance

Check available CPU cores: nproc
Adjust partition count based on cores
Ensure no other heavy processes running
Issue: Spark UI Not Accessible

UI only available during job execution
Run longer jobs or add input() pause in code
Issue: Import Errors

Verify PySpark installation: pip3 show pyspark
Check Python version: python3 --version
Conclusion
In this lab, you:

Optimized Spark jobs by tuning partition counts for your hardware
Implemented caching strategies to accelerate iterative computations
